    "description": "After selling out the first three issues, DC is packaging DARK KNIGHTS OF STEEL #1-3 in a new collection for fans that may have missed their first chance at picking up the superhero fantasy series from writer Tom Taylor (SUPERMAN: SON OF KAL-EL, INJUSTICE) and artist Yasmine Putri (NIGHTWING, THE HELLBLAZER). DARK KNIGHTS OF STEEL: THE GATHERING STORM will be available at comic book shops on Monday, March 1, 2022.\n\n",
